# fastclean

ðŸš€ CLI tool for creating FastAPI projects with Clean Architecture

## Quick Start

```bash
# Install
pip install -e .

# Create templates
make templates

# Create a new project
fastclean init --name=my_api --db=postgresql --docker

# Generate CRUD
fastclean crud Product --fields="name:str,price:float"
```

